            <h2>Become a Validator Sponsor</h2>
            <p class="donation_info">
              We invite organizations and individuals that support Web standards to become validator Sponsors and earn recognition as a driving force behind valued community tools.</p>
            <p class="donation_info">Sponsors receive acknowledgement for their support on the Validators' sites as well as this page, for a year. The terms of this sponsorship match those described in the <a href="http://www.w3.org/Consortium/supporter-policy#policy_misc">Miscellaneous section of the W3C Supporters Program policy</a>.</p>
            <p class="donation_info">
               Please <a href="mailto:&#x76;&#x61;&#x6C;&#x69;&#x64;&#x61;&#x74;&#x6F;&#x72;&#x2D;&#x64;&#x6f;&#x6e;&#x61;&#x74;&#x65;&#x40;w3.org">Contact Us</a> about this opportunity.
            </p>
